description: TEHRAN – Iran has displayed the home-grown Mohajer 6 drone at a defense expo in the Iraqi capital Baghdad.

description:
The Palestinian Health Ministry has accused Israel of “deliberately obstructing” healthcare services for Palestinians in the occupied West Bank.
 “This policy constitutes a flagrant violation of international humanitarian law and exacerbates the suffering of civilians,” it said.

description: TEHRAN - The 24th week of the Iran’s Persian Gulf Pro League (PGPL) concluded with victories for both Esteghlal and Persepolis, maintaining the Blues' one-point lead at the top of the table. With just six matches remaining, the title race is heating up, leaving fans on the edge of their seats.
title: Title chase heats up in Persian Gulf Pro League
